name: mo_pack
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.2.0" %}

package:
    name: mo_pack
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: v{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://github.com/SciTools/mo_pack/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
    md5: c8dbbabd2a267c1e7457c2f0603e7838

build:
    number: 0
    skip: True  # [win]

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - numpy x.x
        - setuptools
        - cython
        - libmo_unpack
    run:
        - python
        - numpy x.x
        - libmo_unpack

test:
    imports:
        - mo_pack

about:
    home: https://github.com/SciTools/mo_pack
    license: LGPL-3.0
    summary: Python wrapper to libmo_unpack

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - pelson
        - ocefpaf
